<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-indent: 32px;color: black !important">桃李满园香，骊歌再响起。6月24日清晨，江西软件职业技术大学隆重举行了2023届毕业典礼暨学士学位授予仪式，共同见证学校1920名毕业生顺利完成学业。学校用一场盛大的仪式为同学们的大学生涯画上圆满句号，也为他们新的人生篇章送别、扬帆。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A25%3A56%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8715.png?Expires=2003048757&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=KH%2BUjDCrLO3rjCNzO0uomVCHhBk%3D" width="700" height="402.5" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 700px; height: 402.5px;" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">“蓄势扬帆，风劲潮涌破浪行”</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">今年毕业典礼延续一贯的温情，又处处彰显不一样的特色。学校将满满的心意寄予在独家定制的现场氛围布置和明信片中。“锋锋”“香香”元素的门型展架和签名墙、江软元素拍照框、各类DP打卡点惊艳亮相，掀起了师生、家长的合照打卡的热潮。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A27%3A05%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8716.png?Expires=2003048826&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=MIOLX5yCtApvTrlNxmhv9ump12M%3D" width="700" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 700px; height: 700px;" height="700" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">24日清晨，迎风招展的旌旗、整齐划一的学士服、青春洋溢的笑脸，空气中充盈着喜悦和热情。全体在家校领导、中层干部、教职工代表、毕业班辅导员、本科毕业生代表及家长代表在热烈的氛围中出席典礼。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">典礼在全体起立奏唱《中华人民共和国国歌》中拉开了帷幕。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">典礼由执行校长范红铭主持。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A27%3A45%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8717.png?Expires=2003048866&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=gW4j9CgZ0SdUCr6ZBnybmq3WN9s%3D" alt="" width="700" height="531" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 700px; height: 531px;" border="0" vspace="0" title=""/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-indent: 2em;color: black !important">中国工程院院士、先锋软件学院名誉校长倪光南通过视频为同学们送上祝福。他深情寄语同学们：跨出校门后，投身于建设社会主义现代化强国的大潮中，树立远大的理想，矢志报国，坚定前进信心，立大志、明大德、成大才、担大任，努力成为堪当民族复兴重任的青年。以积极的心态做向</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-indent: 2em;color: black !important">阳花木，相信自己，迎接挑战，做事脚踏实地、实事求是，以行动去挖掘自己的能力和价值，在人生的道路上披荆斩棘，书写青春的最美篇章。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A30%3A12%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8718.png?Expires=2003049013&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=FMy470FT3OcFPfKFzavvKPY2Wac%3D" alt="" width="700" height="448" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 700px; height: 448px;" border="0" vspace="0" title=""/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-indent: 32px;color: black !important">倪光南院士近年来致力于在中国推广Linux和有自主核心技术的、非 Wintel架构的网络计算机（NC），是我国发展具有自主知识产权的IT产业的灵魂性和旗帜性人物。作为学校名誉校长，他执着于为国家培养技术技能人才。自2004年起，或线上或线下，倪光南院士从未缺席一届毕业典礼。他殷切希望同学们牢记责任和使命，为这个伟大的时代奉献激情、智慧和汗水；树立“学好软件、报效祖国”的信念，为实现中国梦、为建设科技强国贡献自己无悔的青春。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">“风乍起，合当奋意向人生”</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">&nbsp; &nbsp;陈方平理事长在典礼上分享了先锋软件集团和学校的创业历程，并从“以史为鉴，增强底蕴”“创业创新，勇闯新路”“传承文化，共赢未来”三个层面寄语毕业生。他希望学校培养的毕业生是有理想、有追求、有担当、有作为、有品质、有修养的“六有”大学生，走上社会是栋梁之才，走进企业是高层次高素质技术技能人才，成立家庭是顶梁柱。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A31%3A40%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8719.png?Expires=2003049101&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=Q%2B%2BiW2g6UsYx0HrWc%2F6aO745LG0%3D" alt="" width="700" height="517" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 700px; height: 517px;" border="0" vspace="0" title=""/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><br style="box-sizing: border-box"/>&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-indent: 32px;color: black !important">校党委书记、督导专员江延湖在典礼上宣读了《关于准予刘瑜等1917 名学生按期毕业的决定》《关于授予梅兰等 1917 名学生学士学位决定》《关于表彰 2023 届“优秀毕业生”等的决定》。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A33%3A06%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720.png?Expires=2003049187&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=evAnkEZUMa4RqwOdzgLS9wU27jQ%3D" alt="" width="700" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 700px; height: 562px;" height="562" border="0" vspace="0" title=""/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-indent: 2em;color: black !important">庄力可校长激励同学们践行学校“创业创新，知识管理”的校训，在未来勇于创新，敢于担当，在实践中锤炼自己，成为真正的创新者。最后他为毕业生们献上“此生尽兴，赤诚善良”“生如逆旅，一苇以航”的箴言，祝愿即将踏上新的人生旅程的同学们“拔剑千山过，归来仍少年”。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A33%3A54%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8721.png?Expires=2003049235&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=8EhRZGJ%2FfqhvromSEqJ3a7xdEkA%3D" alt="" width="700" height="595" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 700px; height: 595px;" border="0" vspace="0" title=""/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">“当风轻借力，一举入高空”&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">2006届软件技术专业毕业生校友张成龙生向母校和辛勤工作的老师们表达了最衷心的感谢和最崇高的敬意。他向即将踏上人生新征程的2023届毕业生们分享了自己的心得体会。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A34%3A26%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8722.png?Expires=2003049267&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=h74HVZc%2B0IcwJxKkLbZ9biJk0UE%3D" alt="" width="700" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 700px; height: 444px;" height="444" border="0" vspace="0" title=""/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">“不要害怕未来，因为未来是由你们自己创造的。”教师代表罗磊表达了对同学们的期望和鼓励，“我们要发扬毅力、勤奋刻苦、锐意进取、敢于拼搏、乐观向上等优良品质，在未来的道路上书写属于自己的华丽篇章。”</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A34%3A58%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8723.png?Expires=2003049299&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=iNsxW4dZ%2BYXP8ipW%2FcwqUdAMKMw%3D" alt="" width="700" height="576" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 700px; height: 576px;" border="0" vspace="0" title=""/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-indent: 32px;color: black !important">&nbsp;毕业生代表郑乐馨回顾了美好的四年大学时光，并表示不论今后身处何地，都会铭记“学好软件，报效祖国”的誓言、“创业创新，知识管理”的校训，用青春和汗水诠释江软学子最美的模样。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A35%3A36%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8724.png?Expires=2003049337&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=cSf5d5RSDQ6qwO1kVPdhIVqV7tc%3D" alt="" width="700" height="510" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 700px; height: 510px;" border="0" vspace="0" title=""/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21.3333px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-indent: 42.6667px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-align: center">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-indent: 2em;color: black !important">&nbsp;校领导为优秀毕业生代表颁发了荣誉证书。这是对毕业生们四年来努力的肯定，同时也是对他们未来的期盼。在学士学位授予仪式环节中，学士学位