ne-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-indent: 32px;color: black !important">典礼在陈方平理事长领唱的《再见》和校歌《先锋之歌》中落下帷幕。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A41%3A37%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8731.png?Expires=2003049697&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=KZdYgzZK1q8sUGim22jwlqtkfHM%3D" alt="" width="700" height="325" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 700px; height: 325px;" border="0" vspace="0" title=""/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">“长风破浪会有时，直挂云帆济沧海”</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-indent: 2em;color: black !important">本次典礼，学校通过线上同步直播，使未能到现场的毕业生、老师、学生、校友和家长通过云端共同见证毕业典礼盛况。</span></p><p><br/></p><section data-role="outer" style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">江西软件职业技术大学是全国第一所软件职业技术大学，是全国首批本科层次职业教育改革试点学校。自办学以来，学校深耕职业教育，秉承创业创新、知识管理的校训，实施校企融合、产学互动的办学模式，实践三好一专、十一工程人才培养体系，专注软件技术及相关专业的人才培养。形成了用企业家育人理念培养学生、请工程师当老师、拿真实项目进行实训的校企深度融合发展思路。学校始终践行学习的先锋、运动的先锋、快乐的先锋、创新的先锋、劳动的先锋“五个先锋”校园文化，“学好软件，报效祖国”的理想信念、“创业创新，知识管理”的校训。学校围绕区块链等新一代信息技术，在智慧城市、交通、能源、卫生、教育等领域，为社会累计培养了十万余名软件优秀人才。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">从江西软件职业技术大学顺利毕业的、全国首批获得四年制本科职业教育毕业证和学士学位证的毕业生们即将踏出校门，他们所拥有的专业知识和职业技能将在未来的工作中发挥重要作用。这是学校职业本科教育迈入新台阶的又一里程碑，是党和国家亲切关怀的结果，也是数代职教人共同努力的结果。这批毕业生的就业表现和综合素质将为职业教育的本科化提供宝贵的参考和借鉴，进一步提升职业教育的地位和形象。对我国职业本科教育试点工作意义重大。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p></section><p><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-size: 16px !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A42%3A44%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8732.png?Expires=2003049765&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=zwfdp%2FNzaqz2ry4IoHd4lvb7NWI%3D" width="700" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 700px; height: 437.5px;" height="437.5" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/></span></span></p><p><br/></p>